Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:54.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:00.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:15.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:20.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:24.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:27.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:28.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:38.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:44.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:52.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:54.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:00.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:15.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:20.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:24.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.83,0:01:27.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:28.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.67,0:01:38.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:44.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:52.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:53.69,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:22:01.49,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:07.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.47,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.97,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:28.16,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.44,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.98,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:54.32,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:53.69,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:22:01.49,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:07.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.47,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.97,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:28.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:33.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:37.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:45.98,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:54.32,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該出去的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是正式的圖書部成員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你們是擅自在這裡進行無關的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有部員資格的人能出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些礙事的東西扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這貨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  touch  me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去  滾出去  滾出去  滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但道理在他們那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能在大圖書館活動只是因為有圖書委員長的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒得到正式許可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來圖書部變回原來的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你幹的好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的活動室被佔了  很是困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是為他們排憂解難
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒人煽動  他們是一直都不會露面的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賤人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道牧羊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.53,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}通過和圖書部對決，\N你將飛得更高。\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說牧羊人會指引人到達理想的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是想讓這個學園變得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個副會長搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是來吵架的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的地方竟然被那種人搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  失去的只是個活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人都還能聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺會說話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把水無祭辦成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄的話就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓那個副會長得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部員資格算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  Project在哪裡都能繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的牽絆並沒斷掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她好好瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她好瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多岐川同學有牧羊人支持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我問了小太刀  她說完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀也說  不一定真是牧羊人的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  筧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們活動室裡有陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我跟你說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  今天晚飯想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  筧和我一起成為牧羊人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水無祭什麼的兩三下就能解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是學生會主辦的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水無祭的日期時間一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些出場嘉賓是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是校友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是以畢業生和在校生的交流為主題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續宣傳  為水無祭拉客…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申請退票的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有什麼好點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}再擴大宣傳範圍如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的  難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水無祭時白崎會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該對大家說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果說了  水無祭可能會中止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我可以阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易準備的飯  你卻不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正常道歉會讓我困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想當牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然該選這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會被遺忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會把你這個人完全忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這關乎著白崎的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  我之所以會不想被遺忘  也是多虧他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然發展成這種結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆跟我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你之間  只有一個能成為牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直想妨礙你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們發了郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導了圖書部的成立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還盡量撮合你和當中的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓你無法成為牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣我也姑且算是牧羊人的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會選擇讓你不幸的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管跟圖書部的誰走到一起  你都能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就  出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你下定決心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想變得跟父親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我最希望得到幫助的時候  父親什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有可以拯救的方法  那我就要選擇它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的決斷  我表示由衷的敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會把它…消除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在筧同學生日的時候  我想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有筧同學在  我們也許就可以無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候筧同學說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是將近兩個月前的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕對不能忘記的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  筧同學他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  白崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學他…要消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  白崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你還在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始  和你說過的話越來越記不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕這樣下去會全部忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是白崎你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進屋裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是寶貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟你在一起的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不可能忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  求你了  跟我說實話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考慮這事很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候起  我一直很憧憬牧羊人所在的魔法圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我也帶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為牧羊人的話  就會被眾人遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那筧同學你…覺得沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真的能夠讓他人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就證明那時的孤獨和絕望…都是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你認為  非要成為牧羊人才能帶來幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你根本不相信Happy  Project  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更討厭成為了牧羊人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終有一天會從白崎的記憶中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她討厭我吧  這樣的話就不用傷得那麼深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的先決問題是  尋找拯救白崎的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長  大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉她…千莉她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園  佳奈助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御…御園？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要馬上進行治療
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡？  還是這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助來電話說你大事不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找佳奈的話  她就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我嗎  筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳…佳奈助？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長他嫌一個人服侍他不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長你真好色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止讓多少女人流淚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該懲罰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡開始懲罰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你們到底搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈說  要挽留男人的話還是只能用美色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上是說男人都好這口的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼網站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挽留？挽留誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然就是學長你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧！到底是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給我到日光浴食堂來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上  我們所有人都收到了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧京太郎賣身給學生會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易內容是  他加入學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此換取水無祭被認定為學園的正式活動並成功舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏還是賣身給學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜傻瓜傻瓜傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會讓學長你到學生會那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放棄望月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我們沒用  要讓你一個人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}不  都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎  你也來說他兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會加入學生會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是多岐川捏造了事實發給你們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們上當了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  通過這次的事情  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是  我們這些人不能少了任何一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大家在一起才是Happy  Project嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧  白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要在其他書裡找才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我看到你往這裡走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長  請讓我在水無祭的舞台上唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是只有唱歌這一條路走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為其他人  而是為大家的話  我感覺自己可以歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  是我希望自己能再次歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長你早就預料到會有這種未來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  這是御園你自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水無祭嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是小社團聚在一起搞個活動而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過值得報導啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟  據說歌姬御園千莉會出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  御園千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園千莉！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌姬要出場？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園  這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是怎麼傳開的  但是是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  儘管去宣傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈  對不起讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家至今為止的辛勞  絕對不能白費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  Project  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芹澤水結的After  School  Avenue
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}　　　　　放學路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天請來的特別嘉賓是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在汐美學園最受歡迎的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎緒美同學和御園千莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說你們要和學生會主辦的活動一較高低
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為他們的活動也是非常有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我們也會努力做好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說御園同學你也會上台歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證會讓大家欣賞到比入學典禮上更好的巔峰表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水結  我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（水無祭的司儀將會是芹澤水結！）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們越是掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就越能證明我是正確的  只會有這個結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  我們Happy  Project…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們Happy  Project…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們Happy  Project…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學你這個…笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去白崎她會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:25.42,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H252F4D&\pos(270,53.333)}水無祭預熱節目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想了解一下大家對水無祭的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備萬無一失  放手一搏足矣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鈴木嘔心瀝血創作的劇本已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經迫不及待想要唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫不及待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來Happy吧~！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我通宵想出來的酷炫台詞還…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.54,0:23:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水無祭期待你的參與
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參與
